53
00:03:19,320 --> 00:03:21,150
first of all, there must be a sound

54
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:22,430
and aesthetic mood.

55
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:23,760
With your hands behind your back,

56
00:03:24,390 --> 00:03:25,870
land yourself elegantly,

57
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:28,110
revealing your transcendent silhouette

58
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,670
before turning your head slightly.

59
00:03:32,590 --> 00:03:33,270
For self-introduction?

60
00:03:33,710 --> 00:03:34,110
No.

61
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,550
This is just the preliminary.

62
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,480
Wait until everyone

63
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,870
exclaims,

64
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,390
in a leisurely tone, you said,

65
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,480
"I'm sorry

66
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,590
