81
00:04:28,790 --> 00:04:29,640
"I am"

82
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,520
"I am"

83
00:04:32,030 --> 00:04:33,470
"Mr. Liu Yue."

84
00:04:34,350 --> 00:04:35,270
"Fairy

85
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:37,710
Luoxia?"

86
00:04:38,470 --> 00:04:40,030
That's right.

87
00:04:40,030 --> 00:04:40,880
You practice it first.

88
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:43,830
In front of you?

89
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,440
