93
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,590
You

94
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,590
may ask for advice

95
00:04:54,590 --> 00:04:55,680
from Martial Uncle Luo Xuan.

96
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,230
