101
00:05:05,960 --> 00:05:07,390
I shall make my move.

102
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,390
You practice first.

103
00:05:30,270 --> 00:05:31,080
I am

104
00:05:31,390 --> 00:05:32,560
Fairy Luoxia.

105
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,000
I am

106
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,320
Fairy Luoxia.

107
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:38,680
I am

108
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:41,880
Fairy Luoxia.

109
00:05:45,790 --> 00:05:47,390
This is too embarrassing.

110
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,830
Why am I actually practicing?

111
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,520
Right.

112
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:10,390
Why am I

113
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:15,000
actually practicing?

114
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:22,220
[Penglai Pavilion]

115
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,590
Young Lady.

116
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:44,960
You have become

117
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,120
a disciple of the Academy,

118
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:47,120
why is it

119
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:50,000
that you still bear Sky's Beyond
in mind?

120
00:06:51,150 --> 00:06:52,790
I deserve your grudge

121
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:56,030
for not taking action according to plan.

122
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:02,320
Young Lady, you are exaggerating.

123
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:03,710
I dare not to.

124
00:07:04,790 --> 00:07:06,390
I was going to look for all of you

125
00:07:06,390 --> 00:07:07,830
after sending Baili Dongjun

126
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,080
to Qinglong Gate that day,

127
00:07:09,150 --> 00:07:10,270
but I didn't expect

128
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,000
that Mr. Liu Yue would take me in.

129
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,790
I came to see you today

130
00:07:14,470 --> 00:07:15,760
as soon as I found an opportunity.

131
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,320
But

132
00:07:19,790 --> 00:07:21,390
why didn't you

133
00:07:21,390 --> 00:07:22,470
bring Baili Dongjun

134
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,390
to the path where Yuji was on that day?

135
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:27,000
That day, after several
assassination attempts,

136
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:28,350
Baili Dongjun's nerves

137
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,830
had reached a state of extreme tension.

138
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:31,390
If he really went down that path,

139
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,590
met Yuji,

140
00:07:33,590 --> 00:07:35,030
got defeated and taken away by us,

141
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,390
with his character,

142
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,640
Xunian Art aside,

143
00:07:40,470 --> 00:07:41,710
I'm afraid that he'd just
search for an opportunity

144
00:07:41,710 --> 00:07:42,910
to go down with us.

145
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,350
This is the first reason.

146
00:07:44,790 --> 00:07:45,390
Secondly,

147
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,560
I'm wondering

148
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,830
if this is really the only way

149
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:55,150
to restore the kingdom.

150
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:55,830
What do you mean?

151
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,710
No.

152
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,150
I don't have any better plans yet.

153
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,230
We'll talk about it later.

154
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:07,590
Qixuan, I have to go now.

155
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:10,030
I will continue
to observe Baili Dongjun.

156
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:13,440
I will contact you

157
00:08:14,590 --> 00:08:15,640
once I make a decision.

158
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:17,270
As for Yuji,

159
00:08:18,230 --> 00:08:19,470
