160
00:08:26,470 --> 00:08:27,030
Young Lady.

161
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:30,880
Is there anything else?

162
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:33,280
Should I

163
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:35,040
tell you

164
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:36,590
about the innate martial artist?

165
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:41,870
Nothing.

166
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:48,080
Please take good care of yourself,
Young Lady.

167
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,080
Is this really the only way

168
00:08:58,280 --> 00:08:59,920
to restore the kingdom?

169
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,350
Young Lady.

170
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:08,440
What exactly are you planning to do?

171
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:13,350
Yue Qing.

172
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:23,800
Master?

173
00:09:52,400 --> 00:09:52,830
