anything to do with me?

180
00:10:18,990 --> 00:10:20,560
I was just really bored

181
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:22,080
and wanted to play weiqi with you.

182
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:30,160
Master...

183
00:10:31,110 --> 00:10:32,440
We may play weiqi now.

184
00:10:37,110 --> 00:10:37,560
Come.

185
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:38,870
Let's play it.

186
00:10:47,830 --> 00:10:49,230
That's more like it.

187
00:11:10,350 --> 00:11:11,960
Yun, this is for you.

188
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:17,040
What's this?

189
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,830
My mother has started
teaching me needlework.

190
00:11:20,350 --> 00:11:22,590
This is the first pouch I embroidered.

191
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:28,350
Wenjun, this is so beautiful.

192
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,200
I like it very much.

193
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:43,560
Even if I could predict
everything in the world,

194
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:46,960
I could not foresee our reunion.

195
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:50,200
I didn't expect it to be like this.

196
00:12:52,590 --> 00:12:53,400
Tell me some stories

197
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:54,400
about the outside world.

198
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:57,320
I'll let you go when you're done.

199
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,960
I haven't left this place
in a long time.

200
00:13:13,230 --> 00:13:14,960
Just like this dish called Caged Bird,

201
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:17,870
although I'm caged,

202
00:13:19,280 --> 00:13:20,160
I yearn

203
00:13:22,230 --> 00:13:24,110
for the outside world.

204
00:13:36,110 --> 00:13:37,560
I wonder if she will be willing

205
00:13:38,590 --> 00:13:40,920
if I suggest taking her out.

206
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:24,230
You're back.

207
00:14:28,590 --> 00:14:30,630
I met Young Lady during the day.

208
00:14:33,470 --> 00:14:35,510
What was her explanation?

209
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,350
I will explain

210
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:40,710
the details to you later.

211
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,350
However, there's one thing
that we can confirm.

212
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:45,560
She has not betrayed Sky's Beyond.

213
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:48,800
That's good.

214
00:14:49,400 --> 00:14:50,400
Are there any other instructions

215
00:14:50,990 --> 00:14:52,110
from Lord Wuxiang?

216
00:14:53,590 --> 00:14:56,320
He instructed us to give a great gift

217
00:14:59,710 --> 00:15:00,800
to the imperial family of Beili.

218
00:15:03,560 --> 00:15:04,040
What?

219
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:08,110
You're saying that Ye Dingzhi is Ye Yun?

220
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,110
The son of Ye Yu, Ye Yun?

221
00:15:14,990 --> 00:15:16,990
No wonder he didn't want
the imperial jade seal.

222
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:19,160
No wonder he said
I can definitely provide him

223
00:15:19,630 --> 00:15:20,870
with what he wants.

224
00:15:21,830 --> 00:15:22,870
What he wants is

225
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:25,080
my life.

226
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,230
Prepare the horses. Now!

227
00:15:31,470 --> 00:15:32,960
I am going to the palace.

228
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:13,080
Good morning, Ye Dingzhi.

229
00:16:16,470 --> 00:16:17,040
Good morning, miss.

230
00:16:25,350 --> 00:16:27,630
You are not done
with the previous story.

231
00:16:28,510 --> 00:16:30,440
We are talking about
the Buddhist States today.

232
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:31,680
Sure.

233
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:33,440
Give me a minute,

234
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,750
I'm going to wash up.

235
