Let's talk about the Buddhist States.

257
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,750
One must pass by a city
named Biluo City

258
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,640
to go to 32 Buddhist States
in the Western Regions.

259
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:07,200
On the way to Biluo City,

260
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:07,960
one will pass through

261
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:09,550
a small town called Sangu Town.

262
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:11,710
It is also known as
the town of belles.

263
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:14,270
One visit makes you mesmerized,
two visits make you captivated,

264
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:14,990
three visits...

265
00:18:15,070 --> 00:18:15,600
Wait,

266
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:17,600
are there many belles there?

267
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:18,880
Yes.

268
00:18:20,230 --> 00:18:21,680
I don't want to hear it. Next story.

269
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,680
Let me tell you

270
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,790
about the characteristics of Sangu Town.

271
00:18:28,470 --> 00:18:29,440
Sangu Town

272
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:30,840
is actually established

273
00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:31,680
by some merchants.

274
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,270
There are plenty of gambling houses,

275
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:34,790
the largest one is called Belle's Manor.

276
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,600
Belle again?

277
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:38,640
Can't we skip this?

278
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,680
I'm talking about the gambling house.

279
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:41,640
Why is called

280
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,920
Belle's Manor?

281
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,120
Because there are many belles there.

282
00:18:44,680 --> 00:18:46,070
The person in charge of
the largest gambling house

283
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:47,750
is a courtesan

284
00:18:47,990 --> 00:18:48,920
named Tiannv.

285
00:18:50,710 --> 00:18:52,600
Even a courtesan is brought up.

