00:18:55,470 --> 00:18:56,550
I'll stop talking about it.

287
00:18:57,550 --> 00:18:59,120
That is what I heard from others.

288
00:18:59,310 --> 00:19:00,680
I have never been to Belle's Manor.

289
00:19:04,470 --> 00:19:06,920
After passing through Sangu Town,

290
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:08,360
you will arrive at Biluo City.

291
00:19:09,030 --> 00:19:09,920
This city

292
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:11,270
has a very big temple

293
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:12,200
named Jiulong Temple.

294
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:17,160
Accessories for sale.

295
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:24,960
Xuan,

296
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:27,030
is the book that interesting?

297
00:19:27,860 --> 00:19:29,060
[Xie Xuan, Mr. Qingxiang
of Eight Young Masters of Beili]

298
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:29,710
Mr. Li.

299
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:34,710
You haven't answered my question yet.

300
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,470
There are countless books in the world.

301
00:19:39,070 --> 00:19:40,400
Even if I were to read non-stop

302
00:19:40,470 --> 00:19:41,270
without resting

303
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,840
until the moment of my death,

304
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:44,360
I still could not finish reading
all the books in this world.

305
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,310
For me,

306
00:19:46,640 --> 00:19:47,640
this will be my biggest regret.

307
00:19:48,270 --> 00:19:49,470
To reduce it,

308
00:19:49,680 --> 00:19:50,840
I can only seize the time

309
00:19:50,840 --> 00:19:51,600
to read more books.

310
00:19:53,360 --> 00:19:54,230
Some people became bookworms

311
00:19:54,230 --> 00:19:55,840
from reading too much.

312
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,680
However, if one reads so many books

313
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:59,600
that even a hundred bookworms combined

314
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,470
couldn't surpass the amount,

315
00:20:02,030 --> 00:20:03,680
then perhaps one could become
a Scholarly Deity.

316
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:06,840
Kid,

317
00:20:06,990 --> 00:20:07,920
how can your master

318
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:08,990
compare to me?

319
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:10,440
He doesn't know martial arts

320
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:11,640
nor does he have fame.

321
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:13,120
You might as well follow me.

322
00:20:14,030 --> 00:20:14,680
How about this?

323
00:20:15,160 --> 00:20:16,360
I'll make an exception for you.

324
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:17,680
Although I have already accepted

325
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:18,510
my last disciple,

326
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:19,880
you can still

327
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,790
become my last, last disciple.

328
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:22,960
You'll be the lastest of all.

329
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:23,880
What do you think?

330
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:24,600
I don't want to.

331
00:20:26,880 --> 00:20:28,680
You haven't read as many books
as my master.

332
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:30,310
Who said that?

333
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:31,030
I am

334
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,270
at least twice his age.

335
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:33,070
I have walked past so many more bridges

336
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:33,790
than the roads

337
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:34,640
he has travelled.

338
00:20:34,710 --> 00:20:36,790
The books I have read are definitely

339
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,160
slightly

340
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,470
more than the ones he read 20 years ago.

341
00:20:44,070 --> 00:20:45,550
I have better martial arts skills
than him.

342
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:48,550
I can just learn martial arts
from books.

343
00:20:49,470 --> 00:20:50,160
You are

344
00:20:50,230 --> 00:20:51,600
probably the only person

345
00:20:51,710 --> 00:20:52,470
in this world

346
00:20:52,510 --> 00:20:53,880
who refuses to be my disciple.

347
00:20:54,470 --> 00:20:55,640
That's an exaggeration, Mr. Li.

348
00:20:56,640 --> 00:20:58,640
You may go ask
the farmers in the fields,

349
00:20:58,880 --> 00:20:59,990
the courtesans in brothels,

350
00:21:00,230 --> 00:21:01,880
or the wealthy young masters
lounging in their homes,

351
00:21:02,270 --> 00:21:03,070
all of them are probably not willing

352
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:03,990
to be your disciple.

353
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:06,360
Each person has their own way of living.

354
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,600
Not everyone

355
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:09,030
has an interest in swordsmanship.

356
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,200
Fine.

357
00:21:10,230 --> 00:21:10,990
I can't argue with you.

358
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,470
Are you not missing out on anything

359
00:21:13,470 --> 00:21:14,270
for your trip?

360
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:16,790
No worries, Mr. Li. I won't.

361
00:21:17,550 --> 00:21:18,440
Good.

362
00:21:19,400 --> 00:21:21,310
Let's go. I'll send you off.

363
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:22,160
Let's go.

364
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:25,930
[Diaolou Tavern]

365
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:29,400
Seniors,

366
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:31,510
have the two of you ever

367
00:21:32,550 --> 00:21:33,920
seen each other face-to-face
with the veils lifted?

368
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:37,400
Dongjun, this is not called a veil.

369
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:38,790
Dongjun,

370
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,270
you should read more books.

371
00:21:43,550 --> 00:21:44,710
Stop avoiding the important issues
and focus on the trivial ones.

372
00:21:45,440 --> 00:21:45,880
By the way,

373
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:46,640
isn't this

374
00:21:46,640 --> 00:21:48,310
the banquet to celebrate my initiation?

375
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:49,960
We're here at Diaolou Tavern

376
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:50,600
which I've been thinking of visiting.

377
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,200
Will there be Qiulubai?

378
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:56,470
Qiulubai is only available once a month.

379
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:58,030
I'm afraid there won't be any today.

380
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:00,640
Such a pity.

381
00:22:01,470 --> 00:22:02,640
If I had known,

382
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:03,840
I'd have asked Master
to keep some for me.

383
00:22:07,600 --> 00:22:08,070
By the way,

384
00:22:08,310 --> 00:22:09,600
aren't we going
to ask Master to join us?

385
00:22:17,550 --> 00:22:18,230
Dongjun,

386
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,550
usually,

387
00:22:20,990 --> 00:22:22,790
we can't call him
to join occasions like this.

388
00:22:23,230 --> 00:22:23,920
What occasion?

389
00:22:24,510 --> 00:22:25,120
Why?

390
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:29,160
The less you know, the better.

391
00:22:34,840 --> 00:22:35,840
Didn't I already tell you

392
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,680
not to come in unless I ask for you?

393
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:40,200
There is a guest outside

394
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,920
who has a question for you, sirs.

395
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:42,880
What is it? Shoot.

396
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:45,710
Should you start the feast

397
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:47,270
when Mr. Li isn't here yet?

398
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:54,360
Go, go, go.

399
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:56,600
Run!

400
00:23:05,840 --> 00:23:07,470
Let's drink together.
What are you running away from?

401
00:23:08,640 --> 00:23:09,840
Master.

402
00:23:10,310 --> 00:23:10,710
Sit.

403
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,360
Xuan, you sit down, too.

404
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:19,440
Excuse me.

405
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:21,360
Xie Xuan.

406
00:23:22,030 --> 00:23:22,960
It's been a while.

407
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:30,270
Lei'er, this is...

408
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:31,990
You're being rude.

409
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:32,640
Have a guess.

410
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,680
Do you really think I didn't know?

411
00:23:35,120 --> 00:23:36,230
Since you all know him

412
00:23:36,470 --> 00:23:37,640
and he is invited here by Master,

413
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:39,360
among the Eight Young Masters of Beili,

414
00:23:39,670 --> 00:23:40,460
apart from the unnamed senior

415
00:23:40,470 --> 00:23:41,200
whom I have never met

416
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:42,400
and Third Senior Gu

417
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:43,270
who is far away in Xinan Circuit,

418
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:46,600
only Mr. Qingxiang remains.

419
00:23:48,470 --> 00:23:49,920
Dongba, you're pretty smart.

420
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,200
It has been a while

421
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,470
since I had a drink with you all.

422
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:54,470
This grand gesture

423
00:23:54,470 --> 00:23:56,600
must have been arranged
by Ruofeng, right?

424
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:59,070
Your new junior,

425
00:23:59,230 --> 00:23:59,990
Dongba,

426
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:01,120
just joined us.

427
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:02,790
It should be celebrated indeed.

428
00:24:02,990 --> 00:24:03,790
Feel free to decide

429
00:24:03,990 --> 00:24:04,790
how you want to drink,

430
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:06,030
I'll up for it.

431
00:24:07,360 --> 00:24:08,120
Well...

432
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:15,440
Mr. Li.

433
00:24:17,230 --> 00:24:19,470
Dongjun just joined the Academy today,

434
00:24:19,710 --> 00:24:23,440
I think we should just forget it.

435
00:24:26,880 --> 00:24:27,750
How can we do that?

436
00:24:28,230 --> 00:24:29,840
Here, let us toast for Master together.

437
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:34,640
Dongba, great.

438
00:24:35,470 --> 00:24:36,440
Come, cheers.

439
00:24:36,550 --> 00:24:36,920
Cheers.

440
00:24:37,230 --> 00:24:38,710
Drink up.

441
00:24:41,790 --> 00:24:42,880
This is good liquor.

442
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,160
Ruofeng, listen.

443
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:48,640
The most important thing for a man

444
00:24:48,710 --> 00:24:50,230
is his status.

445
00:24:51,790 --> 00:24:52,640
Whenever I went to Baihua Hall,

446
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,310
Li Xinyue would

447
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,790
help me pay the bill.

448
00:24:57,990 --> 00:24:58,680
That is great.

449
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:03,710
Senior.

450
00:25:04,990 --> 00:25:05,600
Dongjun,

451
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:09,030
you know now

452
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:13,160
why we

453
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,920
refrained from asking Mr. Li to join us.

454
00:25:20,230 --> 00:25:22,400
Never forget the dreams
of the human world for hundreds of years,

455
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:24,530
drink thousands of cups
without getting drunk

456
00:25:24,530 --> 00:25:26,160
to attain immortality.

457
00:25:29,750 --> 00:25:31,160
Poetry Deity wrote this
for me exclusively

458
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,440
back in the day.

459
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:37,030
Why are you all drunk already?

460
00:25:37,360 --> 00:25:38,160
This is no fun.

461
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:39,960
Dongba,

462
00:25:40,070 --> 00:25:41,470
I knew you'd hold your liquor.

463
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:43,360
Here, have a drink with me.

464
00:25:44,270 --> 00:25:45,400
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

465
00:25:46,790 --> 00:25:47,360
I can't.

466
00:25:55,470 --> 00:25:56,440
After leaving Jiulong Temple,

467
00:25:56,440 --> 00:25:57,310
you'd arrive at the Buddhist States.

468
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:58,880
Speaking of the Buddhist States,

469
00:25:58,920 --> 00:25:59,470
when I was there,

470
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:01,070
I took a monk as my Zen Master

471
00:26:01,270 --> 00:26:02,360
and learned Buddhism
for one month.

472
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,640
After that,

473
00:26:05,120 --> 00:26:06,310
I met my current master,

474
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:08,120
who is a sword master

475
00:26:08,510 --> 00:26:09,360
from Nanjue.

476
00:26:21,790 --> 00:26:22,710
Master?

477
00:26:23,840 --> 00:26:24,640
Dongba,

478
00:26:25,230 --> 00:26:26,440
since you just joined the Academy,

479
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:27,230
I have

480
00:26:27,230 --> 00:26:28,360
prepared a gift for you.

481
00:26:29,030 --> 00:26:30,600
Really? I'm getting a gift?

482
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:31,840
Of course.

483
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:33,070
I am

484
00:26:33,070 --> 00:26:34,440
the Mr. Li who never lies.

485
00:26:34,920 --> 00:26:35,550
Xuan.

486
00:26:45,120 --> 00:26:46,710
Drink 30 cups of liquor in a row,

487
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,400
and your inner force and aura

488
00:26:49,400 --> 00:26:50,310
will be greatly improved.

489
00:26:51,790 --> 00:26:53,030
This is no ordinary book,

490
00:26:53,030 --> 00:26:54,470
nor is it ordinary liquor.

491
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:56,120
Your former master, Gu Chen,

492
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:57,160
also read this book.

493
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:59,200
I'm giving it to you now.

494
00:26:59,550 --> 00:27:00,270
Keep it well.

495
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:02,990
He's just lending it.

496
00:27:08,040 --> 00:27:10,810
[Liquor Scripture]

497
00:27:13,030 --> 00:27:13,680
Thank you, Master.

498
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,120
Thank you, Mr. Qingxiang.

499
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:18,960
Now that we're done drinking,

500
00:27:19,440 --> 00:27:20,400
it's time for a fight.

501
00:27:36,270 --> 00:27:37,030
What a strong sword qi.

502
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,710
Look.

503
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:15,440
Someone more pretentious than Xuanliu

504
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:16,640
has finally appeared.

505
00:28:16,990 --> 00:28:18,270
He's making such a big fuss

506
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:19,440
like he's worried that others won't know

507
00:28:19,510 --> 00:28:20,440
his identity.

508
00:28:21,030 --> 00:28:21,710
Master,

509
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:23,360
who is he?

510
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:27,070
He is Rain Demon, the Sword Deity.

511
00:28:27,140 --> 00:28:29,780
[Rain Demon, the Sword Deity of Nanjue]

512
00:28:30,360 --> 00:28:31,360
Li Changsheng,

513
00:28:33,030 --> 00:28:34,030
I haven't seen you in a long time.

514
00:28:34,550 --> 00:28:36,790
I don't think
I'd like to see you much.

515
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:39,310
He... He's a man?

516
00:28:40,230 --> 00:28:41,400
Indeed.

517
00:28:42,310 --> 00:28:42,990
Why...

518
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:44,880
He practices
Demon Deity Sword Techniques.

519
00:28:45,600 --> 00:28:46,640
Here's a rumor related to
Demon Deity Sword Techniques.

520
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:48,310
The sword manual
can only be passed down

521
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:49,510
by mortals who borrowed powers
from a demon god.

522
00:28:49,710 --> 00:28:50,680
Those who practice it

523
00:28:50,710 --> 00:28:51,960
are highly susceptible to backfire.

524
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:53,440
He is the example
of someone who went haywire

525
00:28:53,440 --> 00:28:55,200
when suppressing the strong backfire of

526
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:55,960
Demon Deity Sword Techniques.

527
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:56,680
That is why

528
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,230
despite having a male body,

529
00:28:58,400 --> 00:29:00,360
his face is becoming
more and more woman-like.

530
00:29:02,840 --> 00:29:03,710
Rain Demon,

531
00:29:04,070 --> 00:29:05,680
why did you come all the way

532
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:06,790
from Nanjue?

533
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:08,270
To find someone.

534
00:29:09,310 --> 00:29:10,510
Could it be Ye Dingzhi?

535
00:29:11,920 --> 00:29:12,640
You're aware?

536
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:13,600
Get out of the way!

537
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:20,880
Why are you attacking?

538
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:23,880
Where is he?

539
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:24,640
What he?

540
00:29:24,960 --> 00:29:25,550
Who are you talking about?

541
00:29:26,030 --> 00:29:26,790
Don't play dumb.

542
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:27,840
Ye Dingzhi.

543
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:29,160
Where is he?

544
00:29:29,600 --> 00:29:30,400
Who are you?

545
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,400
Why should I tell you?

546
00:29:32,120 --> 00:29:33,030
I am his master.

547
00:29:34,230 --> 00:29:35,200
If you say so.

548
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:36,960
He came to take the Academy examination

549
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,440
to take Master as his master.

550
00:29:38,960 --> 00:29:39,790
Ridiculous.

551
00:29:48,230 --> 00:29:48,680
Sword Borrowing Technique.

552
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:11,640
What is happening?

553
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:18,440
This is a duel
between two Sword Deities.

554
00:30:18,470 --> 00:30:19,710
It's not just a matter of moves
and techniques,

555
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:22,310
but an unparalleled display
of brilliance

556
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:24,310
that resonates
with the heavens and the earth.

557
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,160
Your Majesty,

558
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:15,680
it's Rain Demon's Mystic Wind Sword.

559
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,230
Father,

560
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:22,680
Rain Demon

561
00:31:22,880 --> 00:31:23,400
must be...

562
00:31:24,070 --> 00:31:25,510
He must be here to find Ye Yun.

563
00:31:26,030 --> 00:31:26,990
The son of that treacherous minister

564
00:31:27,270 --> 00:31:28,550
has been hiding in Nanjue
for many years,

565
00:31:28,790 --> 00:31:30,360
he has since acquired
excellent swordsmanship.

566
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:31,960
He must...

567
00:31:32,680 --> 00:31:34,200
He must be a disciple of Rain Demon.

568
00:31:35,840 --> 00:31:36,600
Father,

569
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:39,030
you can't hesitate any longer.

570
00:31:39,750 --> 00:31:40,790
